	<!-- message -->
	<p>Paladin.<br />
<br />
Stuns and bash to keep shammy from casting. Root for dogdog. Lots of HPs. Can cure all shammy dots. LoH and possibly Soulfire which could amout to 6 complete heals during the fight. Heals. Would be a long one but with no way for shaman to escape Pally would eventually prevail.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
